# --- Terraform state / plan (contains secrets) ---
**/.terraform/
**/*.tfstate
**/*.tfstate.*
**/*.tfplan

# --- Local variable files (often contain secrets) ---
**/*.tfvars
**/*.tfvars.json

# Keep non-secret examples tracked
!**/*.tfvars.example
!**/*.tfvars.json.example

# --- direnv ---
**/.envrc
**/.envrc.local
**/.direnv/

# --- Common env/secrets files ---
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
!**/.env.*.example

# --- Keys / certs ---
**/*.pem
**/*.key
**/*.p12
**/*.pfx
**/*.crt
**/*.cer
**/*.der
**/*.jks
**/id_rsa
**/id_ed25519
**/id_*        # catches weird key names

# --- Logs that might leak ---
**/*.log

proxmox/dev/VM-Backup/
proxmox/dev/ISOs/
proxmox/.secrets/

